# The `data/` rule above is for the root runtime dir (per-visitor SQLite
# session DBs, gitignored for good reason). But it also matches any nested
# `data/` dir by name — including `server/nvm/analyze/data/`, which holds a
# required runtime asset: the emotional-arc lexicon read synchronously via
# readFileSync at module-import time in emotional-arc.ts / inflection-tension.ts
# / theme-extract.ts. Without it, CI's clean checkout throws ENOENT on import
# and 38 server/analyzer/export tests fail. Re-include that one dir explicitly.
!server/nvm/analyze/data/
!server/nvm/analyze/data/**
